# Cursor MCP Configuration for Codegraph

This project has an MCP server for semantic code analysis.

## MCP Server: codegraph

Location: `server/mcp_server/main.py`

Tools available:
- search: Hybrid search (chunks + symbols)
- get_context: Get symbol context (definition, usages, callers)
- graph_slice: Semantic slicing for bug analysis

Usage:
- Type `@codegraph` in chat to use tools
- Example: "@codegraph search authentication logic"

